		"inclusion": "1. Connect the device in accordance with the wiring diagram and switch on the mains voltage.\n2. Set the controller in add mode (see the controller's manual).\n3. Quickly, triple click the key no. 1 (S1) or the B-button located inside the housing.",
		"exclusion": "1. Make sure the device is powered.\n2. Set the controller in remove mode (see the controller's manual).\n3. Quickly, triple click the key no. 1 (S1) or the B-button located inside the housing.",
		"reset": "Within 5 seconds after connecting the mains voltage supply, press once the S1 key and then hold the S2 key.",
